This class helps to create a tree for the PI History in GUI. You should initialize it with a list of piHistoryCategories. Then the whole tree will build by itself, because a PiHistoryCategory contains all child-elements (PiHistoryEntry) as a list. The class also stores the pp and effort, if the stored object is an instance of PiHistoryEntry. Otherwise it will calculate the average pp and effort of child-elements. The PI will be calculated for all kinds of objects.
